"Due to Google's new file storage and reading rules in Android 11 version, affected by this: Android / data and OBB directory files, system and third-party file management can not read, write and display. Therefore, the path entrance is hidden and not displayed."
The changes made to domestic users using Android 11 version are as follows:
"1. Through the file management - all files entry, enter the Android directory, file management can't read, display and operate the files in the data and OBB directory."
2. The original wechat, QQ directly open the document, need to save the file, in the file management view management.
3. Important files of third-party applications can be saved manually or downloaded to local to view and manage.
4. File management is unable to search, display and operate files in related directories.
